embers-bill-on-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fuk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtScuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=ec1c61d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong</a>"},{"pid":"619628fb9bd17cb5b6233ecf965f0221b2bc17f6","tid":2032652,"uid":222907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a3637ee3b75cc148ee771013a8eec36927ec323e","tid":2032652,"uid":156509,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:38:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PChpcm8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPChpcm8.jpg&h=635a5b6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n畫面靚咪吸引到人睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:40:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rnt7UBv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRnt7UBv.png&h=f9287f96&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7f39bc810925b33649dafebd042d54004382155","tid":2032652,"uid":120877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:40:40.000Z","msg":"中共仲笑得出咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d300b74c1b21ad42aab010f2e36fad8e3e8e53b","tid":2032652,"uid":263563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:40:49.000Z","msg":"時機唔同"},{"pid":"ca85b11986bc64bff27649e7288c76c91ea34c8c","tid":2032652,"uid":77880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:40:55.000Z","msg":"估到你會咁講"},{"pid":"acc490231b602bafdd187e325eca4256abd627bf","tid":2032652,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"344bcf291314eed682c6fcc90308c7474efb37e2","tid":2032652,"uid":42340,"like":22,"dislike":25,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T07:25:17.000Z","msg":"靚咪可以出相